Above: Brown checked jacket and solid-brown pants of this
snow suit zip up the front. Made of water-repellent rayon-
and-nylon gabardine. Suit, mittens, cap with visor and ear
muffs, 3-6x, about $25. Weather Winky. Edward's, Syracuse
